    public class HwComponentImpl
extends HwResourceImpl
implements HwComponent
    An implementation of the model object 'Hw Component'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Kind
    • Dimensions
    • Area
    • Position
    • Grid
    • Nb Pins
    • Weight
    • Price
    • RConditions
    • Powered Services
    • Static Consumption
    • Static Dissipation
    • Sub Components
